OL,3,CCCTV shows 'frightening' moment masked
OL,4,Crobber aims gun at petrol station
OL,5,Cworker
OL,7,FA man has been jailed after pointing a
OL,8,Fgun at a cashier and robbing a petrol
OL,9,Fstation in Wrexham.
OL,11,FCCTV footage shows the moment Corey
OL,12,FLi, 23, pointed a firearm at a worker
OL,13,Fand then fired it to one side, as he
OL,14,Fand an accomplice raided the premises.
OL,16,FLi targeted the petrol station on
OL,17,FWrexham Road, Rhostyllen, Wrexham, in
OL,18,Fthe early hours of 9 June and demanded
OL,19,Fthe worker opened the till, police
OL,20,Fsaid.
