OL,7,FInvestigating officer Detective
OL,8,FConstable Andrew Vaughan said: "This
OL,9,Fwas an incredibly frightening and
OL,10,Fdistressing experience for the victim,
OL,11,Fwho was threatened at gunpoint as he
OL,12,Fwent about his work.
OL,14,F"Incidents of this nature are very
OL,15,Frare in Wrexham, and I have no doubt
OL,16,FWrexham is a safer community with Li
OL,17,Fbehind bars.
